{"fadein":1.5,"once":true,"id":"BUZHIHUO3","fadeType":2,"mode":2,"fadeOut":1.5,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"sequence":[["Shiranui, the Do-It-All Shopkeeper\n\n<size=45>Chapter 3: The Shopkeeper's Little Buddies<\/size>",1]],"stopbgm":true},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"black":true,"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0]},"side":2,"bgm":"story-1","say":"Port - Supply Shop","dir":1,"bgmDelay":2,"flashout":{"black":true,"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1]}},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"On this day off, I once again concealed myself next to the shop, quietly observing the situation.","dir":1},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Please,  Shiranui, just think about the deep bond we used to share, and let me interview you!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":303030},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":1,"say":"I don't remember ever doing anything with you that would resemble a \"deep bond.\"","paintingFadeOut":{"time":0.5,"side":0},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","actor":301180},{"side":0,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Unapproachable and mysterious, the ghostly owner of the Supply Shop- this interview is gonna sell like hotcakes!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":303030},{"side":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"If you used your segment to promote my shop, I might consider it.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301180},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":0,"action":[{"number":2,"x":0,"type":"shake","delay":0.2,"dur":0.2,"y":45}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"No problem! Let's get started right away!","actor":303030},{"side":0,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"First and foremost, those disheveled animal ears on your head! Is it true that the ghosts make you wear them like that?","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":303030},{"side":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"... I bumped them a few times while organizing things. I thought it'd be a waste to replace them, so I didn't bother getting them fixed.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301180},{"side":0,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Uhh... the rumor that you're actually a ghost... Is it true?","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":303030},{"side":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Are you an idiot?","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301180},{"side":0,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"What about that will-o'-wisp circling you?!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":303030},{"side":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"That's just a floating prop that I got from Akashi because it looked cool.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301180},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":0,"action":[{"number":3,"x":0,"type":"shake","delay":0,"dur":0.15,"y":45}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"Th-then... the rumor that you can see ghosts as well...?","actor":303030},{"side":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I suppose that does happen every now and then.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301180},{"side":0,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Ah, so that's also a fabrica-","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":303030},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":0,"action":[{"number":3,"x":0,"type":"shake","delay":0,"dur":0.1,"y":45}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"Ehhh??? It's true?!","actor":303030},{"side":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"It's true. For example, there's one crawling up your back right now...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301180},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"action":[{"number":3,"x":0,"type":"shake","delay":0,"dur":0.1,"y":45},{"x":-1800,"type":"move","delay":0.6,"dur":0.3,"y":0}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"Waaaaaaaaaaaaahhhh!","actor":303030},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Of course, that's just a lie...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301180},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"However, our very existence already defies the laws of science. It shouldn't be strange at all to see strange things.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301180},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Today, I feel like I learned a bit more about another side of Shiranui.","dir":1},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"However, I feel like she just shot a glance over here. It's just my imagination... right?","blackBg":true,"dir":1}]}